snippet: Investors are “digesting some of those gains from last week and positioning themselves so they’re not too far extended if fourth-quarter earnings slip a bit,” an equity strategist said.
abstract: Cautious investors pull Standard & Poor's 500-stock index down from its five-year high.
lead_paragraph: Investors are “digesting some of those gains from last week and positioning themselves so they’re not too far extended if fourth-quarter earnings slip a bit,” an equity strategist said.

headline.main: Cautious Day Pulls S.&P. From Its 5-Year High
headline.print_headline: Cautious Day Pulls S.&P. From Its 5-Year High
